00b5a8b3f3baa140e839dacdf81dd9f5"><div class="view-content"><div class="views-row views-row-1 views-row-odd views-row-first views-row-last"><div class="views-field views-field-field-podcast"><div class="field-content"><a href="https://www.thenakedscientists.com/sites/default/files/media/Naked_Oceans_12.12.21.mp3" data-title="Considering the future of the oceans" data-audio="https://www.thenakedscientists.com/sites/default/files/media/Naked_Oceans_12.12.21.mp3" class="track"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-play" aria-hidden="true"></span>Play</a><a href="https://www.thenakedscientists.com/sites/default/files/media/Naked_Oceans_12.12.21.mp3" download="Naked_Oceans_12.12.21.mp3" class="ajax-exclude"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-download" aria-hidden="true"></span>Download</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="panel-separator"></div><div class="panel-pane pane-block pane-addtoany-addtoany-button pane-addtoany" ><h2 class="pane-title"> Share</h2><div class="pane-content"> <span class="a2a_kit a2a_kit_size_24 a2a_target addtoany_list" id="da2a_1"> <a class="a2a_button_email"></a><a class="a2a_button_facebook"></a><a class="a2a_button_linkedin"></a><a class="a2a_button_twitter"></a><a class="a2a_button_google_plus"></a><a class="a2a_button_pinterest"></a> </span>
